  "title": "Temp Temperature Screeners #HYNT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Conduct non-contact temperature screenings using provided equipment</p></li><li><p>Politely greet individuals and explain the screening process</p></li><li><p>Identify and respond appropriately to elevated temperature readings following company procedures</p></li><li><p>Maintain confidentiality and professionalism at all times</p></li><li><p>Sanitize screening equipment and work area between uses</p></li><li><p>Accurately document screenings as required</p></li><li><p>Report concerns or incidents to a supervisor immediately<br /><br /><a href=\"https://employer.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/jobs/contract-finance-executive-hynt-recruit-express-4b362a49692dfbac3e98a5394fa8f6f4/view#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Please send your resume to rehealth@recruitexpress.com.sg.</a></p><p>We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>Chloe Impens| Outsourcing Team<br />EA License Number: 99C4599<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd | Company Reg. No. 199601303W<br /></p></li></ul>",
